cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the software and the associated paper (see 'preferred-citation')."
title: "Endofullerene zigzag chain DMRG code"
abstract: >-
  Julia/ITensor code for density matrix renormalization group (DMRG)
  calculations of dipolar molecules (LiF, D2O, H2O) confined in bent
  ("zigzag") endofullerene chains, computing ground and excited states as a
  function of chain angle and effective dipole moment together with the
  associated observables (energies, von-Neumann entanglement entropy, dipole
  and center-of-mass correlations, Binder parameters, net polarization, and
  orientational/radial distributions).
type: software
license: MIT
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-07-08"
